    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels. Six factors flagged as epistemic gaps (not-assessed). Despite the Not Accepted regulatory decision recorded in the base COU, the UoA decision record reflects acceptance of the credibility evidence package as a complete and documented submission — the gaps are transparently enumerated and Monte Carlo UQ has been performed on flow-field inputs. The package is accepted as a credibility evidence record suitable for regulatory submission with documented deficiencies.",
